        <div class="tpgroup_header">
            <span>Today's Top Posts</span>
        </div>
        <div class="post">
            <div class="post-detail d-flex">
                <div class="p-header">
                    <div class="p-title">
                        <span>Odin the Omnipotent</span>
                        <span class="p-date">27/07/022</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-menu">
                        <i class="bi bi-caret-left p-menubtn"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="p-body">
                    After his father’s death, Odin was not going to be so peaceful. Old ways died as the new skyfather born.
                </div>
